column5: Nope they missed us but thanks for checkin we are both doing fine as the weather circles around us.  Art
We are good here Paul,Thanx for askin Joe
What took you two so long to answer??? I was worried sick  Joey
Yeah...you can't pick up a phone???
I haven't met Joe or Art, but I'm sure they'd keep their families safe during a tornado.  They might lose their stuff to strong winds, but their lives would be protected.
Good to hear you and your families are OK Joe /Art !Seems like you have had your share this year. How close were they ?
Way south of us,I have a couple of buds down there but haven't heard from them. Joe
glad to hear you guys are ok, hope it all has passed through.  jason
That's good to hear.  Just saw it on the news this morning in Southern Virginia, so I was thinking this was south of you guys.  Scarey stuff none the less ... hope nobody was hurt.
Glad your ok! Isn`t all of Virginia southern?
Those Virginia tornadoes made the 7:00 AM news on the tube up here this morning too.  Unbelievable destruction and good to hear you boyz came out OK.
... and their girlfriends... uh... er... goats too!!!
